data.name: LDGYL
data.value: select town as 统计单位,convert(decimal(18,2),mj) as 本年度国家公益林面积,convert(decimal(18,2),mj0) as 上年度国家公益林面积 ,convert(decimal(18,2),mj-mj0) as 增加 ,convert(decimal(18,2),cq) as 长期减少 ,convert(decimal(18,2),fw) as 设施减少 ,convert(decimal(18,2),ls) as 临时减少 ,convert(decimal(18,2),wf) as 违法减少 ,convert(decimal(18,2),hl) as 毁林减少 ,convert(decimal(18,2),dmj) as 本年度地方公益林面积,convert(decimal(18,2),dmj0) as 上年度地方公益林面积 ,convert(decimal(18,2),dmj-dmj0) as 地方增加 ,convert(decimal(18,2),dcq) as 地方长期减少 ,convert(decimal(18,2),dfw) as 地方设施减少 ,convert(decimal(18,2),dls) as 地方临时减少 ,convert(decimal(18,2),dwf) as 地方违法减少 ,convert(decimal(18,2),dhl) as 地方毁林减少 from (select (case when grouping(code_table.CNAME) = 1 then '全县总计' else ISNULL(code_table.CNAME,'null') end) as town,grouping(code_table.CNAME) as isgroup, SUM(case when SHI_QUAN_D='10' then MIAN_JI else 0 end) as mj, SUM(case when SHI_QUAN_D like '2%' then MIAN_JI else 0 end) as dmj, -- 长期占用 sum(case when (Q_DI_LEI not like '9%') and DI_LEI like '9%' and YDZL='1' and SHI_QUAN_D='10' then [MIAN_JI] else 0 end ) as cq, sum(case when (Q_DI_LEI not like '9%') and DI_LEI like '9%' and YDZL='1' and SHI_QUAN_D like '2%' then [MIAN_JI] else 0 end ) as dcq, -- 直接为林业生产服务 sum(case when (Q_DI_LEI not like '9%' and Q_DI_LEI not like '8%') and DI_LEI like '8%' and SHI_QUAN_D='10' then [MIAN_JI] else 0 end ) as fw, sum(case when (Q_DI_LEI not like '9%' and Q_DI_LEI not like '8%') and DI_LEI like '8%' and SHI_QUAN_D like '2%' then [MIAN_JI] else 0 end ) as dfw, -- 临时占用 sum(case when (Q_DI_LEI not like '9%') and DI_LEI like '9%' and YDZL='2' and SHI_QUAN_D='10' then [MIAN_JI] else 0 end ) as ls, sum(case when (Q_DI_LEI not like '9%') and DI_LEI like '9%' and YDZL='2' and SHI_QUAN_D like '2%' then [MIAN_JI] else 0 end ) as dls, -- 违法使用 sum(case when ( Q_DI_LEI not like '9%') and DI_LEI like '9%' and BHYY='42' and SHI_QUAN_D='10' then [MIAN_JI] else 0 end ) as wf, sum(case when ( Q_DI_LEI not like '9%') and DI_LEI like '9%' and BHYY='42' and SHI_QUAN_D like '2%' then [MIAN_JI] else 0 end ) as dwf, -- 毁林开垦 sum(case when (Q_DI_LEI not like '9%') and DI_LEI like '9%' and BHYY='50' and SHI_QUAN_D='10' then [MIAN_JI] else 0 end ) as hl, sum(case when (Q_DI_LEI not like '9%') and DI_LEI like '9%' and BHYY='50' and SHI_QUAN_D like '2%' then [MIAN_JI] else 0 end ) as dhl -- from FOR_XIAOBAN_2013 as xb_table inner join T_SYS_META_CODE as code_table on xb_table.XIANG = code_table.CCODE group by rollup(code_table.CNAME) ) as mergeMJ left join (select (case when grouping(code_table.CNAME) = 1 then '全县总计' else ISNULL(code_table.CNAME,'null') end) as town0, SUM(case when SHI_QUAN_D='10' then MIAN_JI else 0 end) as mj0,SUM(case when SHI_QUAN_D like '2%' then MIAN_JI else 0 end) as dmj0 from FOR_XIAOBAN_2012 as xb inner join T_SYS_META_CODE as code_table on xb.XIANG = code_table.CCODE group by rollup(code_table.CNAME) ) as lastMJ on mergeMJ.town=lastMJ.town0 order by isgroup desc --group by rollup(town) --inner join T_SYS_META_CODE as code on MergeMJ.XIANG = code.CCODE group by MergeMJ.town order by MIN(code.ccode),MergeMJ.town

data.name: LDTZ3
data.value: select (select CNAME from T_SYS_META_CODE where CCODE=XIAN and CTYPE='县') as 县,(select CNAME from T_SYS_META_CODE where CCODE=XIANG and CTYPE='乡') as 乡, (select CNAME from T_SYS_META_CODE where CCODE=CUN and CTYPE='村') as 村,XIAO_BAN,XI_BAN, (case when BHYY='42' then wf else 0 end) as wfhj,(case when BHYY='42' and DI_LEI in ('111','112','120','130') then wf else 0 end) as wfyl, (case when BHYY='42' and DI_LEI='301' then wf else 0 end) as wftg,(case when BHYY='42' and (DI_LEI not in('111','112','120','130','301')) then wf else 0 end) as wfqt, (case when BHYY='42' then wf1 else 0 end) as wfhj1,(case when BHYY='42' and DI_LEI in ('111','112','120','130') then wf1 else 0 end) as wfyl1, (case when BHYY='42' and DI_LEI='301' then wf1 else 0 end) as wftg1,(case when BHYY='42' and (DI_LEI not in('111','112','120','130','301')) then wf1 else 0 end) as wfqt1, (case when BHYY='50' then kk else 0 end) as kkhj,(case when BHYY='50' and DI_LEI in ('111','112','120','130') then kk else 0 end) as kkyl, (case when BHYY='50' and DI_LEI='301' then kk else 0 end) as kktg,(case when BHYY='50' and (DI_LEI not in('111','112','120','130','301')) then kk else 0 end) as kkqt, (case when BHYY='50' then kk1 else 0 end) as kkhj1,(case when BHYY='50' and DI_LEI in ('111','112','120','130') then kk1 else 0 end) as kkyl1, (case when BHYY='50' and DI_LEI='301' then kk1 else 0 end) as kktg1,(case when BHYY='50' and (DI_LEI not in('111','112','120','130','301')) then kk1 else 0 end) as kkqt1, JLSJ from ( select XIAN,XIANG,CUN,XIAO_BAN,XI_BAN,DI_LEI,SHSJ,JLSJ,BHYY, (case when BHYY='42' then [MIAN_JI] else 0 end ) as wf, (case when BHYY='42' and SHI_QUAN_D='10' then [MIAN_JI] else 0 end ) as wf1, (case when BHYY='50' then [MIAN_JI] else 0 end ) as kk, (case when BHYY='50' and SHI_QUAN_D='10' then [MIAN_JI] else 0 end ) as kk1 from ZT_LDZZ_2013 where BHYY in('42','50')) as QUERY_RESULT

data.name: LDTZ2
data.value: select (select CNAME from T_SYS_META_CODE where CCODE=XIAN and CTYPE='县') as 县,(select CNAME from T_SYS_META_CODE where CCODE=XIANG and CTYPE='乡') as 乡,(select CNAME from T_SYS_META_CODE where CCODE=CUN and CTYPE='村') as 村,XI_BAN, (case when BHYY like '3%' then ghzj else 0 end) as hj,(case when BHYY like '3%' and DI_LEI in ('111','112','120','130') then ghzj else 0 end) as yl, (case when BHYY like '3%' and DI_LEI='301' then ghzj else 0 end) as tg,(case when BHYY like '3%' and (DI_LEI not in('111','112','120','130','301')) then ghzj else 0 end) as qt, (case when BHYY not like '3%' then qtz else 0 end) as hj1,(case when BHYY not like '3%' and DI_LEI in ('111','112','120','130') then qtz else 0 end) as yl1, (case when BHYY not like '3%' and DI_LEI='301' then qtz else 0 end) as tg1,(case when BHYY not like '3%' and (DI_LEI not in('111','112','120','130','301')) then qtz else 0 end) as qt1, SHSJ,JLSJ from ( select XIAN,XIANG,CUN,XI_BAN,DI_LEI,SHSJ,JLSJ,BHYY, (case when BHYY like '3%' and Q_DI_LEI like '9%' and (DI_LEI not like '9%') then [MIAN_JI] when BHYY like '3%' and (Q_DI_LEI not like '9%') and DI_LEI like '9%' then 0-[MIAN_JI] else 0 end ) as ghzj, (case when (BHYY not like '3%') and Q_DI_LEI like '9%' and (DI_LEI not like '9%') then [MIAN_JI] else 0 end ) as qtz from ZT_LDZZ_2013) as QUERY_RESULT

data.name: LDTZ1
data.value: select dw,xmmc,pzwh,shsj,pzdw, (case when LDYT like '1%' then '基础设施项目' when LDYT='20' then '公共事业和民生项目' when LDYT in('30','40','50','51','52','53') then '经营性项目' when LDYT like '6%' then '城镇、园区建设项目' else '其他' end) as 项目类型, (case when XMLX='1' then '永久占地' when XMLX='2' then '临时占地' when XMLX='3' then '农村集体建设用地' when XMLX='4' then '直接为林业生产服务的工程设施占用林地' else '' end) as 林地性质, ZYBM,ZBHFF,JLSJ,(yl+sl+tg+qg+wcl+mp+cf+hs+yld+qt) as 合计,yl,sl,tg,qg,wcl,mp,cf,hs,yld,qt,(yl1+sl1+tg1+qg1+wcl1+mp1+cf1+hs1+yld1+qt1) as 合计1,yl1,sl1,tg1,qg1,wcl1,mp1,cf1,hs1,yld1,qt1 from ( select (select CNAME from T_SYS_META_CODE where CCODE=XIAN and CTYPE='县') as dw,XMMC,PZWH,SHSJ,(select CNAME from T_SYS_META_CODE where CCODE=SPJB and CTYPE='审批级别') as pzdw, LDYT,XMLX,ZYBM,ZBHFF,JLSJ, (case when BHYY<>'42' and DI_LEI in ('111','112','120','130') then [MIAN_JI] else 0 end) as yl, (case when BHYY<>'42' and DI_LEI='200' then [MIAN_JI] else 0 end) as sl, (case when BHYY<>'42' and DI_LEI='301' then [MIAN_JI] else 0 end) as tg, (case when BHYY<>'42' and DI_LEI='302' then [MIAN_JI] else 0 end) as qg, (case when BHYY<>'42' and DI_LEI='401' then [MIAN_JI] else 0 end) as wcl, (case when BHYY<>'42' and DI_LEI='500' then [MIAN_JI] else 0 end) as mp, (case when BHYY<>'42' and DI_LEI='601' then [MIAN_JI] else 0 end) as cf, (case when BHYY<>'42' and DI_LEI='602' then [MIAN_JI] else 0 end) as hs, (case when BHYY<>'42' and DI_LEI in('701','702','703','704','705','706') then [MIAN_JI] else 0 end) as yld, (case when BHYY<>'42' and DI_LEI not in('111','112','120','130','200','301','302','401','500','601','602','701','702','703','704','705','706') then [MIAN_JI] else 0 end) as qt, (case when BHYY<>'42' and DI_LEI in ('111','112','120','130') then [MIAN_JI] else 0 end) as yl1, (case when BHYY<>'42' and DI_LEI='200' and SHI_QUAN_D='10' then [MIAN_JI] else 0 end) as sl1, (case when BHYY<>'42' and DI_LEI='301' and SHI_QUAN_D='10' then [MIAN_JI] else 0 end) as tg1, (case when BHYY<>'42' and DI_LEI='302' and SHI_QUAN_D='10' then [MIAN_JI] else 0 end) as qg1, (case when BHYY<>'42' and DI_LEI='401' and SHI_QUAN_D='10' then [MIAN_JI] else 0 end) as wcl1, (case when BHYY<>'42' and DI_LEI='500' and SHI_QUAN_D='10' then [MIAN_JI] else 0 end) as mp1, (case when BHYY<>'42' and DI_LEI='601' and SHI_QUAN_D='10' then [MIAN_JI] else 0 end) as cf1, (case when BHYY<>'42' and DI_LEI='602' and SHI_QUAN_D='10' then [MIAN_JI] else 0 end) as hs1, (case when BHYY<>'42' and DI_LEI in('701','702','703','704','705','706') then [MIAN_JI] else 0 end) as yld1, (case when BHYY<>'42' and DI_LEI not in('111','112','120','130','200','301','302','401','500','601','602','701','702','703','704','705','706') then [MIAN_JI] else 0 end) as qt1 from ZT_LDZZ_2013) as QUERY_RESULT

data.name: LDTZ
data.value: select town as 统计单位,convert(decimal(18,2),mj) as 本年度面积,convert(decimal(18,2),mj0) as 上年度面积,convert(decimal(18,2),ghz-ghj+qtz) as 林地增减小计 ,convert(decimal(18,2),ghz-ghj) as 规划调整增减,convert(decimal(18,2),qtz) as 其他增加,convert(decimal(18,2),cqyl+cqtg+cqqt) as 长期减少小计 ,convert(decimal(18,2),cqyl) as 长期减少有林地,convert(decimal(18,2),cqtg) as 长期减少特灌,convert(decimal(18,2),cqqt) as 长期减少其他 ,convert(decimal(18,2),fwyl+fwtg+fwqt) as 设施减少小计,convert(decimal(18,2),fwyl) as 设施减少有林地,convert(decimal(18,2),fwtg) as 设施减少特灌 ,convert(decimal(18,2),fwqt) as 设施减少其他,convert(decimal(18,2),lsyl+lstg+lsqt) as 临时减少小计,convert(decimal(18,2),lsyl) as 临时减少有林地 ,convert(decimal(18,2),lstg) as 临时减少特灌,convert(decimal(18,2),lsqt) as 临时减少其他,convert(decimal(18,2),wfyl+wftg+wfqt) as 违法减少小计 ,convert(decimal(18,2),wfyl) as 违法减少有林地,convert(decimal(18,2),wftg) as 违法减少特灌,convert(decimal(18,2),wfqt) as 违法减少其他 ,convert(decimal(18,2),hlyl+hltg+hlqt) as 毁林减少小计,convert(decimal(18,2),hlyl) as 毁林减少有林地,convert(decimal(18,2),hltg) as 毁林减少特灌,convert(decimal(18,2),hlqt) as 毁林减少其他 from (select (case when grouping(code_table.CNAME) = 1 then '全县总计' else ISNULL(code_table.CNAME,'null') end) as town,grouping(code_table.CNAME) as isgroup, SUM(MIAN_JI) as mj, sum(case when BHYY like '3%' and Q_DI_LEI like '9%' and (DI_LEI not like '9%') then [MIAN_JI] else 0 end ) as ghz, sum(case when BHYY like '3%' and (Q_DI_LEI not like '9%') and DI_LEI like '9%' then [MIAN_JI] else 0 end ) as ghj, sum(case when (BHYY not like '3%') and Q_DI_LEI like '9%' and (DI_LEI not like '9%') then [MIAN_JI] else 0 end ) as qtz, -- 长期占用 sum(case when (Q_DI_LEI like '1%') and DI_LEI like '9%' and YDZL='1' then [MIAN_JI] else 0 end ) as cqyl, sum(case when (Q_DI_LEI='301') and DI_LEI like '9%' and YDZL='1' then [MIAN_JI] else 0 end ) as cqtg, sum(case when (Q_DI_LEI<>'301' and Q_DI_LEI not like '1%' and Q_DI_LEI not like '9%') and DI_LEI like '9%' and YDZL='1' then [MIAN_JI] else 0 end ) as cqqt, -- 直接为林业生产服务 sum(case when (Q_DI_LEI like '1%') and DI_LEI like '8%' then [MIAN_JI] else 0 end ) as fwyl, sum(case when (Q_DI_LEI='301') and DI_LEI like '8%' then [MIAN_JI] else 0 end ) as fwtg, sum(case when (Q_DI_LEI<>'301' and Q_DI_LEI not like '1%' and Q_DI_LEI not like '9%' and Q_DI_LEI not like '8%') and DI_LEI like '8%' then [MIAN_JI] else 0 end ) as fwqt, -- 临时占用 sum(case when (Q_DI_LEI like '1%') and DI_LEI like '9%' and YDZL='2' then [MIAN_JI] else 0 end ) as lsyl, sum(case when (Q_DI_LEI='301') and DI_LEI like '9%' and YDZL='2' then [MIAN_JI] else 0 end ) as lstg, sum(case when (Q_DI_LEI<>'301' and Q_DI_LEI not like '1%' and Q_DI_LEI not like '9%') and DI_LEI like '9%' and YDZL='2' then [MIAN_JI] else 0 end ) as lsqt, -- 违法使用 sum(case when (Q_DI_LEI like '1%') and DI_LEI like '9%' and BHYY='42' then [MIAN_JI] else 0 end ) as wfyl, sum(case when (Q_DI_LEI='301') and DI_LEI like '9%' and BHYY='42' then [MIAN_JI] else 0 end ) as wftg, sum(case when (Q_DI_LEI<>'301' and Q_DI_LEI not like '1%' and Q_DI_LEI not like '9%') and DI_LEI like '9%' and BHYY='42' then [MIAN_JI] else 0 end ) as wfqt, -- 毁林开垦 sum(case when (Q_DI_LEI like '1%') and DI_LEI like '9%' and BHYY='50' then [MIAN_JI] else 0 end ) as hlyl, sum(case when (Q_DI_LEI='301') and DI_LEI like '9%' and BHYY='50' then [MIAN_JI] else 0 end ) as hltg, sum(case when (Q_DI_LEI<>'301' and Q_DI_LEI not like '1%' and Q_DI_LEI not like '9%') and DI_LEI like '9%' and BHYY='50' then [MIAN_JI] else 0 end ) as hlqt -- from FOR_XIAOBAN_2013 as xb_table inner join T_SYS_META_CODE as code_table on xb_table.XIANG = code_table.CCODE group by rollup(code_table.CNAME) --code_table.CNAME,xb_table.XIANG ) as mergeMJ left join (select (case when grouping(code_table.CNAME) = 1 then '全县总计' else ISNULL(code_table.CNAME,'null') end) as town0, SUM(MIAN_JI) as mj0 from FOR_XIAOBAN_2012 as xb inner join T_SYS_META_CODE as code_table on xb.XIANG = code_table.CCODE group by rollup(code_table.CNAME) ) as lastMJ on mergeMJ.town=lastMJ.town0 order by isgroup desc --group by rollup(town) --inner join T_SYS_META_CODE as code on MergeMJ.XIANG = code.CCODE group by MergeMJ.town order by MIN(code.ccode),MergeMJ.town
